Package: sess
Type: Package
Title: Modern R IPC Server
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Gemini
Maintainer: Gemini <gemini@example.com>
Description: Implements a high-performance IPC (Inter-Process Communication) mechanism for R, replacing legacy file-system watchers with raw byte streams. This package provides a generic protocol for IDEs and other clients to communicate with an R session via Unix Domain Sockets or Windows Named Pipes.
